Package edu.uiowa.cs.warp

Class Warp

java.lang.Object
edu.uiowa.cs.warp.Warp
public class Warp extends Object
Warp.java Creates and visualizes elements of the WorkLoad class, populates with appropriate system parameters and configuration values. Can also create a channel scheduler and intercept/report schedule conflicts as well as direct and report on flow reliability, deadlines. Created by Steve Goddard Modified by Dell Harbaugh and Sixuan Liu 02/07/2024
Version:
1.7
Author:
sgoddard
